<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue/FF> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/conformsTo> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/applicationschema/lunom> <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue:1> .
