<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue/BE> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#narrower> <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue/BEM> <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue:1> .
<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue/VSPE> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "In the zoning plan, as far as special zonings are not determined, the significant conditions for spatial planning, like planned state- and federal highways, must be visualized."@en <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue:1> .
<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue/BE> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/conformsTo> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/applicationschema/lunom> <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue:1> .
