<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue/BE> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Def. VBG"@de <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue:1> .
<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue/VSPE> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "INSPIRE governance level: national-technical"@en <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue:1> .
