<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue/FS> <http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#status> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/registry/status/valid> <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue:1> .
