<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue/VBE> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "VBE" <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue:1> .
<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue/V> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Vorbehaltsfläche"@de <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue:1> .
