<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue/BW> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "building zone - residential area"@en <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue:1> .
