<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue/FG> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "In the zoning plan, as far as special zonings are not determined, the significant conditions for spatial planning, like forest areas, must be visualised."@en <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue:1> .
<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue/VSP> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "traffic area - street planning"@en <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue:1> .
