<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue/BEB-II> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "INSPIRE governance level: national-technical"@en <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue:1> .
