<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue/VF> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Areas and the associated facilities can be determined as traffic areas"@en <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue:1> .
<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue/V> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "In building zones, future development areas or open spaces (base zoning), such areas can be determined, that serve purposes of common needs or are expected to be needed within 20 years fo these purposes (reserved area). The intended use has to be determined in the zoning plan."@en <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue:1> .
<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue/VBE> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Verkehrsfläche Bahn Ersichtlichmachung"@de <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue:1> .
