<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue/BEK> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept> <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue:1> .
