<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue/BEW> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "future development zone - residential area"@en <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue:1> .
<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue/BB> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "building zone - operating area"@en <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue:1> .
<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue/BEW> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "BEW" <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue:1> .
